text.section:
This subtitle does not prohibit a credit grantor, in connection with a loan to a nonconsumer borrower, from:
Extending or deferring all or any portion of any scheduled payment under the loan;
Permitting prepayment or refinancing of the loan in whole or in part;
Charging and collecting any charges in connection with the matters referred to in paragraphs (1) and (2) of this subsection; or
Charging and collecting late or delinquency charges, attorney's fees, or collection charges.
